{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_BishopDoBlur}}
'''A_BishopDoBlur'''

(no parameters)

Prepares some values for [[A_BishopSpawnBlur]].  Randombly chooses a value between 3 to 5 blurs and plays the sound BishopBlur on the BODY channel.  In addition it will randomly thrust the actor in one of three directions.  47% chance to the left, 51% to the right, and 2% of the time forwards.

This code pointer is restricted to {{Class|Bishop}} and actors inheriting from it.

